{"tid":2216830,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"反蒙面法17歲少年旺角堵路 認罪判感化1年","createTime":"2020-09-25T03:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T04:36:29.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"15de425f866a80943c22a54c028ac21cf497c0ec","tid":2216830,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T03:59:40.000Z","msg":"去年10月5日《禁蒙面法》生效當天，多區均有示威活動。17歲少年在旺角染布房街以垃圾袋、垃圾桶及回收箱堵路，事後被控。少年早前承認在公眾地方造成阻礙及無牌管有無線電通訊器具兩罪，案件今於西九龍裁判法院判刑。辯方求情指感化官報告正面，少年有悔意，父母亦有到庭支持兒子，望裁判官判處感化令。主任裁判羅德泉終判被告接受12個月感化，其間被告須於晚上9時30分至翌早6時宵禁。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情指，被告的感化及社會服務令內容正面，被告年紀尚輕，對自己的行為有悔意，9月開學後亦有「跟足功課」。感化官建議判處被告感化令12個月，以監督被告的表現。羅官接納感化官建議，判處被告1年感化令。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200925/UWVSBASAIVFLBGUFU72TCEJSX4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200925%2FUWVSBASAIVFLBGUFU72TCEJSX4%2F&d=6i5jd82mnfhmr%2B7rEyOheOBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=26f8678d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200925%2FUWVSBASAIVFLBGUFU72TCEJSX4%2F&h=b982af9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200925/UWVSBASAIVFLBGUFU72TCEJSX4/</a>"},{"pid":"9ee287274cd880d8c1fc0334f8e997a1ed73ad11","tid":2216830,"uid":305767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T04:09:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3f437a8a5ba631efe283084ee64288a9d373ddc","tid":2216830,"uid":264326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T04:15:26.000Z","msg":"推撚到口臭先得2500人，快d簽啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3e32b4x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3e32b4x.pn